---
title: Lobster Ravioli and Shrimp with Heirloom Tomatoes and Tarragon Cream Sauce
description: As far as we’re concerned, lobster anything is cause for celebration. So break out your best plates and light some candles, because these ravioli are filled with it. Continuing the crustacean theme, we’re also folding in succulent shrimp. And because every pasta deserves a good sauce, we’re coating the whole dish in an herby cream sauce studded with bites of juicy heirloom tomatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w19-premium-49b41f82.jpg
